window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sometimes, before you can rise up, you must descend first.</b></p> <p>They have beaten the dungeon. Now they are launched out into a cold universe. The remnants of humanity need to find a new home. They will meet alien races. Some will be allies. Some will need to be killed.</p> <p>Nothing worth doing is ever easy, but Jay has accepted his place and will take charge of their destiny.</p>"; 
